<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Shift Cancelled</h2>
    <p>
    	This is to confirm that the shift that was assigned to you has been cancelled.
    </p>
    <p>
      <% if @shift.response_status == "Auto Rejected" %>
        Note that shift which are <b>not confirmed within 30 mins</b> are <b>automatically cancelled</b>, so in the future please try and confirm assigned shifts at the earliest.
      <% end %>

      <% if @shift.response_status == "Rejected" %>
        The cancellation was done as you had rejected this shift.
      <% end %>
	</p>
	<%= render partial: "shift" %>
  </body>
</html>